      <title>7-Eleven 亿万富翁继承人将从收购中获得巨额回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/7-eleven-billionaire-heirs-would-see-big-payday-from-shock-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果 Seven &amp; i 控股公司（拥有 7-Eleven 便利店）的亿万富翁家族支持这项日本公司史上最大规模的外资收购案，他们将获得巨额回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/7-eleven-billionaire-heirs-would-see-big-payday-from-shock-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 18:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
